{"id":128053,"type":6,"name":"百年虚云","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/5c/99/128053_J3jj0.jpg","summary":"　　二十集电视连续剧《百年虚云》是以中国近代禅门宗师虚云长老心坚行苦，慈悲济世的一生为蓝本而编剧的故事。 \r\n　　1840年，一个风雨交加的夜晚，泉州知府萧玉堂夫妇中年得子，不料生下一个肉团。萧夫人惊骇而亡，萧玉堂悲愤交加，命仆人将这一肉团丢弃。一药翁飘然而至剖开胞衣，一声惊天动地的啼哭，虚云就这样来到了人间，由此开始了他长达一百二十年，经历四十八奇的求道旅程。 \r\n　　本剧通过富于禅机禅趣、曲折生动、真诚感人的故事情节，展示虚云长老难行能行、难忍能忍，为法忘躯的一生。通过离尘出家、觉悟之路、庚子西行、重振鸡山、藏汉弥兵、佛心护国、慧灯长明等七个部分，再现百年难遇的一代高僧的传奇经历。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>百年虚云</li><li><span>集数: </span>20</li><li><span>开始: </span>2009-10-29</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>中国大陆</li><li><span>导演: </span>陈家林</li><li><span>主演: </span>李起厚 / 尹治 / 斯琴高娃</li>","eps":[{"id":500380,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/500380","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":500381,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/500381","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":500382,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/500382","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":500383,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/500383","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":500384,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/500384","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":500385,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/500385","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":500386,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/500386","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":500387,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/500387","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":500388,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/500388","type":0,"sort":9,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":500389,"url"